<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateContainer.UnbindStateBuffer" Title="UnbindStateBuffer method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateContainer">IStateContainer</PageRef> ->
    UnbindStateBuffer
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>UnbindStateBuffer</TypeRef> method removes a previously defined binding to an <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateBuffer">IStateBuffer</PageRef>
      object.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void UnbindStateBuffer(StateBufferId stateBufferId);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="StateBufferId!cobalt.graphics.StateBufferId" Name="stateBufferId">
          The <TypeRef>StateBufferId</TypeRef> of the state buffer to unbind
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
